title: ELEMENT 'CLIP #1' NYJAH HUSTON TEASER - SKATEBOARDING
description:
In anticipation of the Nyjah Huston video, we will be releasing a new clip, once a week until the video drops on 11.11.11.

The inaugural clip is nothing short of death defying, as one wrong move, and your neck deep in pain. The roll up and ride away conditions are nothing to write home about either, but Nyjah manages to walk the line with of a frontside nosegrind down the double set.

Element presents "RISE & SHINE" - The Nyjah Huston video, available on iTunes worldwide on 11.11.11.

Filmed by:
Cole Mathews
Marc Falkenstien
